UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='The sooner we get these stinking things out of my sight and into their cage, the faster my mood will improve. I wish the Argent Crusade had given the Sunreavers the care of this creature. They\'re enough alike that they ought to be able to understand each other.' WHERE `word_id`=164705; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14090
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='I\'ll let the crusaders know that you\'ve just returned with a fresh load of food while the Silver Covenant was sitting on its heels.' WHERE `word_id`=164710; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14092
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='I knew that Kraken was not a match for the likes of you. Without that Kraken disrupting those boats, those Kvaldir will have no choice but to retreat. Great job, Champion!' WHERE `word_id`=164715; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14095
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='Thanks to you, Kul and the aspirants will live fight the Scourge again. That\'s far from the first time someone\'s had to save Kul from himself. My only hope is that the crusaders can find a better outlet for his enthusiasm than allowing him to impart all of his bad habits to impressionable young aspirants.' WHERE `word_id`=164719; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14096
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='Ah, you\'ve mastered the four totems. You should be proud of your accomplishments so far, young $R, but this is only the beginning of your journey.$B$BHere, accept this gift from the Earthen Ring. Carry this relic with you and you will have the power of all four elements at your command.$B$BContinue your training, friend. Grave challenges are ahead for this world - I can hear it in the wind and feel it in the rumblings of the earth. We must be prepared for the worst.' WHERE `word_id`=164726; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14100
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='The defeat of the drottinn will set the kvaldir to fighting amongst themselves, buying us time to use our advantage. The crusade and the tournament are in your debt, champion.' WHERE `word_id`=164730; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14101
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='You have bought us valuable time to move against the Kvaldir and free the seas of these pests. Once again, the Argent Crusade is in your debt.' WHERE `word_id`=164734; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14102
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='Wonderful!  Another batch of powder! Just between us jewelcrafters, I\'ve been making hand over fist selling "pure titanium" jewelry to the local Dalaran mages. Even with their superior intellect, they aren\'t particularly savvy with their gold. If you get more, I\'ll be here.' WHERE `word_id`=275177; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14103
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='Ornolf\'s crew will want to avenge their leader, but without him, they will be easier to defeat. We must live to carry out our mission, to see Icecrown rid of the Scourge and other evils.' WHERE `word_id`=164737; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14104
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='You are truly an example to all who have gathered beneath our banner, $N. Together, we will show the Scourge that we will not be defeated.' WHERE `word_id`=164740; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14105
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='You have done our fallen brethren a great service and spared us the need to face them again on the field of battle. As our campaign against the Scourge progresses, I find myself thinking about my own fate.$B$BShould I fall, $N, I would want someone like you to do for me what you have done for the spirits of the fallen this day. I could not bear the thought of forcing my own brothers to slay me again and again.' WHERE `word_id`=164745; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14107
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='Crusader, you may have bought those sailors just enough time to escape, Maybe next time, those Silver Covenant and Sunreavers will listen before running head first at the enemy.' WHERE `word_id`=164751; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14108
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='I see you\'ve mastered use of the four totems. You are on your way to becoming one with the elemental spirits, but this is only the beginning of your journey.$B$BHere, accept this gift from the Earthen Ring. Carry this relic with you and you will have the power of all four elements at your command.$B$BYour training must continue! I sense a great many trials lie ahead for this world, and we will need the power of the elements behind us if we are to prevail.' WHERE `word_id`=164756; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14111
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad we\'ve gotten that done. It\'s not the most glorious task in the world, but when we partnered with the Argent Crusade, we promised to do all they asked of us without complaint. Of course, the same cannot be said of the Sunreavers.' WHERE `word_id`=164761; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14112
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='Great job, Champion. The fight continues, but now the Kvaldir know that we do not tolerate such attacks.' WHERE `word_id`=164767; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14136
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='Your actions have shown that we Sunreavers are far better allies to the Argent Crusade than the Silver Covenant and it is we who will be triumphant.' WHERE `word_id`=164769; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14140
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='The sooner we get these stinking things out of my sight and into their cage, the faster my mood will improve. I wish the Argent Crusade had given the Silver Covenant the care of this creature. They\'re going to have to get their hands dirty when the battle for Icecrown Citadel starts and I have a feeling they\'ll prove fragile and fussy allies.' WHERE `word_id`=164771; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14141
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='Kul will live to embarrass himself again. That\'s far from the first time someone\'s had to save Kul from himself. With examples like him, it\'s no wonder most of the aspirants are taking up the habits of the Silver Covenant.' WHERE `word_id`=164774; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14142
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='These look a little worse for wear, but they\'re still edible. The crusaders will be glad to hear that we\'ve had some success. Maybe we can give the half-eaten ones to the Silver Covenant. That would make my day.' WHERE `word_id`=164776; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14143
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='<Girana accepts the prayer book from you.>$B$BThank you. We don\'t always see eye-to-eye with the crusaders, but I\'ve learned a lot from Confessor Paletress in my time here.' WHERE `word_id`=164779; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14144
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='I\'m glad we\'ve gotten that done. It\'s not the most glorious task in the world, but when we partnered with the Argent Crusade, we promised to do all they asked of us without complaint. Of course, the same cannot be said of the Silver Covenant.' WHERE `word_id`=164782; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14145
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='Very good, $N.$B$BNow, the trick is to align the facets just right...' WHERE `word_id`=164786; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14151
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='It seems things are worse than we initially thought. You still made a valiant effort and saved many of The Wavecrest\'s crew\'s lives.' WHERE `word_id`=164791; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14152
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='This is a fine list of deeds, $N!  You are to be rewarded handsomely for your accomplishments.' WHERE `word_id`=164795; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14160
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='The Horde will never be a match for our forces as long as we have people like you on our side, $N.' WHERE `word_id`=164800; -- locales_quest - offerrewardtext : entry=14163
UPDATE `trans_words`SET `content_loc3`='It\'s good to see you, $N! Do you have news from the front?' WHERE `word_id`=164801; -- locales_quest - RequestItemsText : entry=14163
